           README for LTIB (GNU/Linux Target Image Builder)

This directory contains various tools and utilities to build GNU/Linux
target images from various source/binary packages.

The code is licensed under the terms of the GPL (see COPYING).
The documentation is licenced under the terms of the FDL (see doc/COPYING).
The rest of the documentation can be found in the 'doc' directory.

See doc/LtibInstall for installation instructions.

See doc/LtibFaq for answers to common questions.

Please report bugs to : stuarth@freescale.com

